title: What Happens After I Die? - Michael Allen Rogers   epub/mobi
description:
What Happens After I Die? - Michael Allen Rogers   epub/mobi
ISBN-10: 1433533022,  256 pages

Death is the one certainty of life. Most of us feel there's something more to life than what we experience and that somehow existence does not end with death. The Bible tells us that we have 'eternity in our hearts'. What does the Bible say about after life? How do I distinguish biblical promises from sentimental myths? How can I be ready?

Exploring the wonders of heaven while taking an honest look at the realities of hell, pastor Michael Allen Rogers provides us with a clear and accessible summary of all things related to the afterlife. This book is an invaluable resource for anyone seeking to answer the crucial question of what happens after I die?
